data.text:
Many AASHTO standards are available on Knovel as part of Standard Specifications for Transportation Materials and Methods of Sampling and Testing. Tips for searching Knovel

Some pre-2009 AASHTO standards are also available in print.

ASTM Compass includes European-adopted IEC and ISO standards issued by AENOR (Spanish Association for Standardization and Certification). European-adopted IEC and ISO standards are identical to the original IEC or ISO standard. For IEC and ISO standards that have not been issued by AENOR, submit a request.

More information about European-adopted ISO and IEC standards
